Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.81,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew without \Na doubt that I killed—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:12.34,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing can change that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.42,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I decided \Nto come clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.79,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.56,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been two weeks \Nsince that trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:27.04,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}and nobody can remember—\Nbeing a member of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.12,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's been completely forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:35.27,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}and only I, the person involved \Nwith his death, can still remember—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:39.78,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get the feeling it's only \Na matter of time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.77,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why, while I \Ncan still remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.72,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:49.76,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}and how you can \Nstop the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:51.98,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.89,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send them back to death, \Nwhere they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.56,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send the dead back to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:01.95,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how to stop the \Ncalamity once it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:08.96,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,There was a girl who looked like \Nher back in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:11.59,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.94,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:16.19,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Isn't Misaki an only child?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:18.80,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,We weren't in the same class,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.35,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,but I know there was \Nsomeone called Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.29,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.00,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Judging by her address,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.63,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have been \Nin the same school as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.01,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Right? That's why it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.56,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Did she wear an eyepatch \Nover her left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.60,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.40,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Our Misaki lost her eye \Nwhen she was four!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.26,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Huh? That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.04,Sign,Kanji Title,0,0,0,,{\an8\b0\fscx100\fs40\fsp1\c&HF2F2F2&\blur0.6\pos(1087,564)}Tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:13.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is the dead person \Nhere with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The extra person...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.61,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,...is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:28.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:34.58,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:37.07,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I think I fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.09,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Teshigawara? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:45.26,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,May I ask you both a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.76,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Do you know someone \Nnamed Kazami Tomohiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.85,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.34,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Just answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.62,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Do you know Kazami?\NWho is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Of course I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:03.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,He's a class officer and the guy \Nyou've always been stuck with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:05.27,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,And you, Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.37,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,How would I not know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.05,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Fuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.78,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.02,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.13,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I think I fucked up bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:22.97,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.37,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I... I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.80,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I was certain that \Nhe was the extra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.38,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.97,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The extra? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.04,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:37.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.65,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.44,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Why on Earth would \NI lie about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:50.49,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I kept poking at him because \Nhe'd been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:56.28,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,He told me that he didn't remember anything about our childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:59.38,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,That he didn't remember much \Nfrom elementary school, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:04.01,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I prepared myself, and asked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.51,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,"You're not really Kazami, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.63,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,"You're the extra person, aren't you?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:15.64,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,He was alarmed at first, \Nbut then flew into a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:20.31,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,He acted so suspicious that \NI was certain it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:24.87,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,So, like we heard on the tape, \Nif he died—if he "returned to death",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.99,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,we'd all be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.32,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.33,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,...you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.86,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Did you... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.64,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:41.34,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,We had started grappling, and then ended up outside on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.63,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Before I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:47.61,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,...he laid still on the brick floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.95,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,There was blood \Npouring from his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.89,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Then, I got scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.60,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,so I ran down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.89,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I saw you come in here earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:04.64,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,...and you wanted to find out \Nif Kazami was the extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.12,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.20,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I thought that, \Nif the extra died,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:12.10,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,then it'd be as if \Nhe'd never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:16.41,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Since you two said \Nyou know him, though....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.76,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I must have fucked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.22,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakaki. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:25.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You either made a mistake, \Nor he's not really dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.46,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Falling two stories down \Nwouldn't necessarily kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.06,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,You can't see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.60,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,It's past that row of shrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.48,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,We should check to \Nsee if he's alive, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:51.25,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Maejima?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.12,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.62,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Blood...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:45.13,Default,Maejima,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.45,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Were you stabbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.17,Default,Maejima,0,0,0,,I looked... in the dining hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.62,Default,Maejima,0,0,0,,Th-The manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.21,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:21.04,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Maejima! \NWe've gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.67,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Why are you \Nscreaming, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.03,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sakaki! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.36,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.50,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's Maejima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.39,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,He's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.13,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.78,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,He's been stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.79,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,There's also a fire \Nin the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.09,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.84,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The manager's inside, dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.08,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,He was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.12,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The killer must've \Nstarted the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.18,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:46.98,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Did you find Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.69,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:54.57,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.70,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Was that... Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.11,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Sugiura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:05.13,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Get Maejima someplace \Nsafe, and call 119!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.12,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.01,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.52,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,...is mine and Takako's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.86,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.18,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,No way...! Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.92,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako! Where are you? {split}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:38.74,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.97,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.50,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.11,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Have you seen \NSugiura or Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.00,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I saw Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.37,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,He came by my room, covered with mud, his face clouded with anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.63,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,saying that Teshigawara \Nwas acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:58.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.25,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I asked him what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.10,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,but he glared daggers at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.16,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Then I mentioned the tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:07.82,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:14.40,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.78,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,The tape recorder's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.55,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Wha— How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.95,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.20,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Is Kazami in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How's Maejima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.62,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I left him with someone who heard the screams and came by to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:30.54,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.34,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,What on Earth is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:38.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Let's split up and \Nsearch for Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Stop by every room and \Ntell everyone to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.14,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,There's a fire! We need to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.76,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:49.02,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.56,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,A killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.69,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Somewhere inside this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.55,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,There's also a fire \Nin the dining hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.03,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,and we've no clue as \Nto where Kazami went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.05,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Everything's going horribly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.58,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,We have to tell Ms. Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.57,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Ms. Mikami? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.09,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,We're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.47,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.22,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Is that blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.39,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.59,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Do you think something \Nhappened to Ms. Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:37.53,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,H-Hey... maybe we should go outside and call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.78,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.63,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Not until we make \Nsure Ms. Mikami's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.04,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Ms. Mikami...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:20.18,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Who's voice was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.36,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Teshigawara's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.44,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,...and Mochizuki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It came from downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.41,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.43,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.43,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.39,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.72,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.98,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,If you had died too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.52,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.07,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Much like how you \Ncan't live without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.87,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.87,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.21,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.84,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Teshigawara! Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.54,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,M-My leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.73,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Send the dead back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.36,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.61,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Get the fuck out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,"Send the dead back to death"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.34,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How did she know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:06.09,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,She... listened to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.58,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You found it in class 3's \Nold homeroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:12.47,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Ogura told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're looking for a clue \Nto help stop the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.64,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.67,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So someone brought the tape here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:25.21,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yes. Mochizuki did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.92,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,As the head of countermeasures, \NI had to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why does she think Misaki \Nis the dead person, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.84,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Ever since our trip to the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.85,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako's been emotionally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:42.46,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I'm going after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.02,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Akazawa! \NIt's dangerous to go alone!{Take this!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:49.55,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,This is an important announcement from the head of countermeasures to all the students of class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.96,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,The tape you are about to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:57.68,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,was left behind 15 years ago, \Nwhen the calamity was stopped midyear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:07.66,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}—and how you can \Nstop the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.62,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.28,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send them back to death, \Nwhere they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.16,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}Send the dead back to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:19.68,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's how to stop the \Ncalamity once it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.29,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,This is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.34,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,This is how the calamity was \Nstopped midyear, 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.72,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,And, the dead person this year is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.97,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Misaki Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:39.65,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,I know this for a fact because we both went to the same elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.48,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,and her left eye was intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:46.18,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Yet now, she is \Nmissing her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.52,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Do you know \Nwhat this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:53.35,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,It means she was \Nreborn incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.97,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,The Misaki Mei we \Nnow know is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:58.60,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.96,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,...we must kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.61,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,Return the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.31,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,...to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.56,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Return the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.12,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Ms. Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:34.66,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You can't kill your own classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.16,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,But if we send the dead \Nperson back to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.05,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,no one else will have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:41.56,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,If we kill Misaki, \Nthe calamity will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.50,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.81,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,Don't do this! \NYou're making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.22,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,Who the fuck's the \Ndead person, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.78,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.27,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,I... I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.64,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.75,Default,Mikami,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.76,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You fucking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.52,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:32.50,Default,Matsui,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:33.74,Default,Watanabe,0,0,0,,The dead girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.97,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,I'll avenge my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.51,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.04,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.35,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.67,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.03,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.58,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Careful, it's slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.42,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.25,Default,Ogura,0,0,0,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.56,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,Ogura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.03,Default,Tsujii,0,0,0,,They're in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:45.91,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,We're saf—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.91,Default,Kawahori,0,0,0,,Go in from downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.50,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,You really think it's Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.76,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,There's something off about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.50,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:11.81,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,Something smells burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.40,Default,Ouji,0,0,0,,He did say there was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:16.98,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,I don't see any flames, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.36,Default,Saruta,0,0,0,,The dining hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,We should be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.79,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I think it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What on Earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,An explosion in the \Ndining hall, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.07,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Maejima passed out in \Nfront of the dining hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Could Sugiura have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.87,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.92,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,It was probably that old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Old hag...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:23.18,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:24.80,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,...a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.97,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,However, since you're not \Nthe dead one, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.21,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Besides, Izumi seems fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:44.02,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:48.00,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.16,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.66,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.55,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.58,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:41.87,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:47.09,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Misaki Mei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.63,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.17,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,No, Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.00,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Sugiura was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.73,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:58.65,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If the dead person was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,all of these tragic things...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,would end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:19.83,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misaki!
